4)After the 3 rd step,we included the FASTA files in the output and script ,initially we got paired and un paired samples which each has 2 files which is unpaired 1,2.,for the bwa-mem2 process we used paired samples1,2

5) when the erros are fixed in fastqc,timmomatic and bwa-mem2 ,we got the .bam file and it is stored in the output folder in the repo 

6) we created a modules folder , and added fastqc process in fastqc.nf same goes for timmomatic and bwa-mem2.To check the another main.nf file by just using the include path in fastqc,trimmomatic and bwa-mem2 process

